post_text:
A reminder to mail your Pocantico Hills School voting ballot, and remember these 3 steps for your vote to count:
1) SIGN AND DATE the envelope that has your name and address sticker;
2) Place your ballot inside that smaller signed envelope;
3) Include your signed envelope within the outer envelope which is already addressed to the school and is stamped. Mail away!

Your vote remains confidential. #GoPOCO

